Class Dispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • Dispatcher

  • public class Dispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Stephen on 4/13/16. Dispatcher for the OS. Responsible for terminating and loading jobs from/to the CPU. Also signals for the OS to terminate if all jobs are complete.
    Author:
    Stephen
